changelog.headline: AI-Driven UI Optimization
changelog.content: Revamped interface based on user feedback, with dynamic layouts adapting to user behavior. Finally, a UI that knows where you want to click before you do.

changelog.headline: Enhanced Security Protocols
changelog.content: Introduced advanced encryption and anomaly detection algorithms. Now detects unauthorized access attempts faster than a cybersecurity meme goes viral.

changelog.headline: Multi-Language Support Expansion
changelog.content: Expanded AI's language support to 25 new languages, including Klingon (by popular demand). Enhanced cultural context comprehension to avoid awkward translations.

changelog.headline: Predictive Analytics Integration
changelog.content: Added AI-powered predictions for user trends and personalized recommendations. It's almost like the app knows you better than you know yourself.

changelog.headline: Improved Natural Language Understanding
changelog.content: Enhanced AI's ability to comprehend complex user queries with higher context awareness and faster response time.
